About this item

  • RELIEVES STRESS: The active holistic herbs of Nuubu Detox foot patches are known to remove toxins, which will drastically improve your physical and mental health.

  • 100% NATURAL INGREDIENTS: The Nuubu detoxification patches feet contain holistic herbs from remote East Asian mountains. Ginger powder and bamboo vinegar are known for their detox properties to clean the body and lift the mood.
  • TRADITIONAL WISDOM: According to Asian knowledge, the human body has over 360 acupuncture points, of which over 60 are on the soles of the feet. The Nuubu Detox foot patches for detoxification treatments combine proven Asian techniques with an elegant, modern approach.
  • EASY TO USE: Stick the Nuubu detoxification patch on the centre of the foot. The soft side of the plaster must have skin contact. It is recommended to apply the Detox plasters before going to bed. Remove the plasters after 6-8 hours, wash your feet and enjoy increased well-being.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
